datasets.name: c8966ccb
datasets.query: select max(run_timestamp) as last_run_timestamp from CATALOG_NAME.SCHEMA_NAME.TABLE_NAME

datasets.name: 2b37989d
datasets.query:
select
    run_timestamp,
    id,
    query_text,
    warehouse_name,
    avg(duration) as average_duration
from
(
    SELECT 
        duration/1000 as duration,
        metrics.planning_time_ms/1000 as query_planning_time,
        metrics.execution_time_ms/1000 as query_execution_time,
        metrics.compilation_time_ms/1000 as query_compliation_time,
        * EXCEPT(duration, metrics)
    FROM CATALOG_NAME.SCHEMA_NAME.TABLE_NAME
)
group by 1, 2, 3, 4
